;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">基于食品的溯源也是同等道理，&ldquo;一物一码&rdquo;通过采用&ldquo;从源头到终端&rdquo;的追溯模式，对食品供应链全过程的每一个节点进行有效的标识，以实施跟踪与溯源。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;一物一码&rdquo;不仅帮助消费者随时随地使用手机扫码查看产品详细信息，对企业本身还可利用二维码对自身及产品进行更多的宣传活动；对管理机构而言则可促进消费者对虚假信息的举报，有效完善对食品质量、假冒伪劣商品的检测。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, s