t;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">一瓶一码绝不像肉眼看到得那么简单，背后有强大的后台管理系统作为支撑。奖项的分布、中奖概率、中奖时间段、奖品总量等等，都是可以预先设置的。而且，根据促销进行的实际情况，随时调整，如果遇到节日、周末等活动周期，中奖率和奖品可以随时调整，整个促销活动的灵活性大、可控度高。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">三、大数据留存，便于二次销售；</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">采用传统的方式开展促销活动，刮卡情况、中奖情况、顾客数据需要通过经销商渠道获取，厂商很难在第一时间内掌握大数据，而且还会存在造假。并且厂商与经销商之间的微妙关系，让厂商难以及时得到真实有效的数据。但是</span><a href=\"https://www.sao.so/mark\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(56, 185, 207); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" target=\"_blank\">一物一码</a><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">的方式，就可以让消费者的扫码数据、扫码手机、扫码地区、扫码时间、扫码频次等统统记录在系统后台，有了这些数据，企业不仅可以按照数据灵活调整促销策略，还能了解忠诚用户，精准进行二次营销。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">以上几点就是给大家讲诉了有关一物一码</span><a href=\"https://www.sao.so/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(56, 185, 207); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" target=\"_blank\">二维码营销</a><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">在饮品销售上的作用，希望能够帮助大家对一物一码有更深层次的认识。</span>','0','','0','10000','','0','','0','1','|0');
