INSERT INTO `v9_news_data` VALUES('300','<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">如今随着网络的发展，微信的普及，越来越多的企业以及商家利用二维码进行各种营销活动，其中扫码送红包就是一种比较流行的</span><a href=\"https://www.sao.so/\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(56, 185, 207); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;\" target=\"_blank\">二维码营销</a><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">活动！接下来我们就来跟大家来聊聊有关到底该如何玩转品牌二维码红包营销新策略呢？</span>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/touyun/uploadfile/2018/0422/20180422055447954.png\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 416px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">&nbs