, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">二、精准触达消费场景</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">最精准的消费场景触达就是，消费者在哪儿，企业营销活动就在哪儿。产品作为企业与消费者接触频率最高的触点，通过为每一件产品赋予唯一的身份码，打通了企业、消费者之间的沟通渠道。借助微信平台开发的第三方扫码应用系统，则实现了更加符合扫码用户需求的营销场景设计。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">三、营销去乙方化</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">以往的营销代理模式，企业的营销活动是通过企业&mdash;&mdash;营销代理方&mdash;&mdash;消费者的方式进行的，企业无法与消费者进行直接有效的互动沟通，整个环节免不了出现沟通误差。有了一物一码互动营销，企业可以通过产品赋码的方式进行互动营销设计。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">四、提高销售转化能力</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">在这个品牌竞争愈加激烈的时代，消费者购买的产品不再只是产品，而是一个产品线，从产品的选择到购买，再到售后服务、重复购买，当一个企业提供的产品服务更加完善、体验度更好之后，消费者就更加愿意参与到品牌的营销互动中来。一物一码可以清晰呈现消费者的这个购买过程，甚至追溯到产品在销售之前的生产加工、质检入库、仓储运输等环节，更加透明的生产线追溯为消费者提供了更加真实有效的产品信息。这种服务能提升消费好感，增强消费者对产品的信任和购买。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">以上就是对一物一码互动营销优势的介绍，希望能够帮助到大家更好的进行营销推广活动。</span>','0','','0','10000','','0','','0','1','|0');
