ot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">二、二维码技术能防伪吗？</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">有一个误区，许多人以为二维码是一个防伪技术，这个认识是错误的，印刷二维码很简单，只要有印刷机，谁都可以印。普通的二维码喷码或印刷只是 一种数据加密技术。并不具备防伪特点。也许有一种声音，说每一个二维码都不相同即一物一码就能起到防伪效果。这个种说法欠考虑，真正的造假者不会只复制假冒你一枚两枚二维码标签进行伪造。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">三、二维码如何实现防伪功能？</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Simsun, sans-s